name: CARRY ON TRADITION - LIMITED CASSETTE
description:
Check out the "Red Tape", the cassette version of Drewtradition's recently released album, Carry on Tradition. This limited edition cassette was entirely produced by Drewtradition and featuring the likes of by B-Real, Freddie Gibbs, Apathy, Chace Infinite, Ryu, Ras Kass, Young De, El Prez, Planet Asia, Sick Jacken, Krondon, Davinci, Tristate, Damani, and many more! 
Only 250 copies were made!
